9
10 -

ćwiczenie 8
Wstaw właściwe zaimki osobowe lub określniki dzierżawcze.
Alison Bright is 1) [...] cousin. 2) [...] is twenty years old.
3) [...] lives with 4) [...] family in a farmhouse in the country.
5) [...] house is old and very big. Alison's father is a farmer.
6) [...] job is very tiring. Alison helps
7) father every day. 8) [...] start work early in the morning and finish late in the evening.
Alison loves horses. 9) [...] favourite horse is "Sunshine".
Alison is very happy with 10) [...] life on the farm.
