ćwiczenie 9
Podkreśl właściwe słowo.
1 This is the [dog's/dogs] bone.
2 That's [Dad's/Dads'] car.
3 Those are the [man's/mans] gloves.
4 These are the [girl's/girls'] houses.
5 This is [Linda's/Lindas] hat.
1. dog's
2 Dad's
3 man's
4 girls'
5 Linda's

ćwiczenie 10
Przekształć poniższe zdania jak w przykładach.
1 This is my bag. [...].
2 These are her books. [...].
3 This is our car. [...].
4 Those are his shoes. [...].
5 This is your cup. [...].
6 Those are their skates. [...].
1. It is mine.
2. They are hers.
3 It is ours.
4 They are his.
5 It is yours.
6 They are theirs.

